README for appliance-wikitests.tar.gz

This is a set of scripts for running wikitests on an appliance.
It is not a dpkg repository yet, but it has the elements needed

To use this script set

1. tar zxf appliance-wikitests.tar.gz
2. ./prep-wiki-tests
3. source setup-selenium PORT BROWSER SERVER_PLATFORM if you are not using the defaults: 4444 firefox linux
4. source ./do-wiki-tests HOSTNAME.DOMAIN.TLD

will run OSR Testcases with output to file testcases.out from a local /wikitests wiki.

Use tail -f testcases.out to observe the run.
